76561198056300273,Recommended,276810,24671214,"Posted: 2 August, 2016",all,austinb,"I love this game... If you are a Warhammer fan, I'd expect you to have a similar response, though there is a steep learning curve.  Young players (possibly with ADHD ;) complain that the game is too hard at first, but the challenge is part of the excitement and fun.  Once you figure it out, it is addictive!The bugs, long load times, and other problems that players justifiably complained about in earlier reviews have been fixed; the game is now a joy to play.  The Devs care and are responsive to player concerns and questions.All the DLC is worthy too.  Chaos, Skaven, and the Witch Hunters are my favorite factions to play, but they're all distinctive and interesting. Like other reviewers, I'd prefer more character customization options and maps, but those are minor quibbles.  Tip: Make sure you go through the tutorials before you start your first warband.In short, this is one of my all time favorite Warhammer games... I can't stop playing it..."
