 and take a while. there are about 8 different sections for them. half of them are game play tutorials where you learn how to move and fight. the other half are page long instructions on how to navigate the menu and warband management UI. Dont worry, the actual game is way more fun than the tutorials.Overall I wouldnt let the few downsides push you away from this game.  There is just a steep learning curve with a kind of annoying camera . they are fixing the load times."
