own.  Because I had found them largely useless, none of my guys were packing ranged weapons and the only archer who could do something a little bit useful sometimes was wounded.That left me with three choices:1.  Accept every single one of my units as a casualty because I had not lost enough units to voluntarily rout.2.  Start a new warband as the game does not allow for loading previous games.  I am totally fine with this concept.3.  Quit the game because I didn't like the first two options.I chose number three, and that is why I cannot recommend this game."
