 have computers for now!  if you have an 85% chance to do something and fail to do 9 out of 10 times I really don't feel like ""probability"" is being taken into account.  You spend the entire time playing this game shaking your head at damn near everything.  Its not at all enjoyable to play in its current state.  I have tried to be patient as this game develops but the core design seems to be flawed.  in its current state its a waste of time and money."
